Package: shabvizstyle
Type: Package
Title: Personal ggplot2 Style Spec for Scientific Figures
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Shabnam", "Hakimi", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "shabtastic@users.noreply.github.com")
Description: A ggplot2 theme and palette helpers built around viridis-family
    colormaps and the Inter font. Mirrors the Python shabviz-style package so
    figures share visual identity across languages.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    ggplot2 (>= 3.4.0),
    scales,
    viridisLite,
    grDevices,
    systemfonts
Suggests:
    ragg,
    showtext,
    sysfonts
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
